SOUTH AFRICA DAYBOOK: Mondi Posts Earnings, Telkom’s CEO

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s   a n d   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-02-21T05:57:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/south-africa-daybook-mondi-posts-profit-telkom-truworths.html
Mondi Group,  Europe ’s largest maker
of office paper, releases full-year earnings. The company, which
trades its stock in Johannesburg and  London , said on Feb. 10
that it will post full-year earnings per share of between 42
euro cents and 49 cents from a year-earlier loss of 6.5 cents.  To contact the reporters on this story:
